---

<section class="mt-8 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
	<Card color="orange">
		<h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl lg:text-6xl mb-4 dm-serif">About me</h2>
		<p class="poppins">
			Hi, Iâ€™m Valerio and I'm an all-around software engineer located in
			Italy. Selected as expert, I'm working as Technical Project Manager
			at <a
				href="https://innovazione.gov.it"
				class="underline"
				target="_blank">Dipartimento per la Trasformazione Digitale</a
			>, a department of Prime Minister's office. I wrote my first program
			in early 00's using Turbo Pascal. Graduated in Computer Science, I
			started developing Web Application.
		</p>
		<p class="poppins mt-2">
			I'm into software design, Micro-Frontend, Microservices and DDD.
			Today, I'm mainly focussed on software architecture in general. DX
			is another relevant topic for me, testing and using tools to improve
			team performance.
		</p>
		<p class="poppins mt-2">
			I love working with Angular and NX but also with NodeJS and .NET.
		</p>
		<p class="poppins mt-2">
			I got <a
				href="https://www.credly.com/badges/bd4efb9b-18c3-4527-b9c7-09aef51ffa18/public_url"
				class="underline"
				target="_blank">GCP Associate Cloud Engineer</a
			> certification. I got Agile certifications too, <a
				href="https://bcert.me/sztlqvbbd"
				class="underline"
				target="_blank">CSPO</a
			> and <a
				href="https://less.works/certificates/valerio-como-95637545460.pdf"
				class="underline"
				target="_blank">LeSS Basics</a
			>.
		</p>
		<p class="poppins mt-2">
			Sometimes I like <a
				href={TALKS_URL}
				class="underline"
				target="_blank">giving talks</a
			> about Angular and beyond.
		</p>
	</Card>
	<div class="flex flex-col gap-8">
		<Card>
			<h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl lg:text-6xl mb-8 dm-serif">
				Tech radar
			</h2>
			<ul class="flex gap-4 flex-wrap">
				{
					techs.map(({ alt, src, width, height }) => (
						<li>
							<Image
								class="rounded-full"
								alt={alt}
								src={src}
								width={width}
								height={height}
							/>
						</li>
					))
				}
			</ul>
		</Card>
		<Card>
			<h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl lg:text-6xl mb-8 dm-serif">
				What I'm doing
			</h2>
			<ul class="flex gap-4 flex-wrap">
				{
					doing.map((item) => (
						<li class="sanchez">
							<Pill>
								<a
									href={item.url}
									target="_blank"
									title={`Go to ${item.name}`}
								>
									{item.name}
								</a>
							</Pill>
						</li>
